data.title: Great Coffee and Even Better Service!!!
data.text:
Great coffee, cool eclectic interior space and fantastic friendly energetic staff. They have it going on here with great customer service. you'll want to stop by just to say hello and they can pick anybody up from having a bad day.  not to mention they they have some really great tasty brew.

What makes this place so great is the staff - witty, friendly, courteous and just plain genuine people who actually care about you!
